The following account of the <span class="corr" id="xd21e822" title=
"Source: P      nans">P      n      ns is given in the Gazetteer
of Malabar.        The name is perhaps connected with p      n, music.
They follow the makkatt      yam family system (of inheritance from
father to son), and practice fraternal polyandry. In South Malabar
there are said to be four sub-divisions, called Tirurengan,
